HEADWORD: Sib
<hw>Sib</hw> <pr>(s⟦icr⟧b)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>sibb</ets>
alliance, <ets>gesib</ets> a relative. ⟦root⟧289. See
<er>Gossip</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A blood relation.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Nash.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
